Format: https://www.debian.org/doc/packaging-manuals/copyright-format/1.0/
Upstream-Name: liblzma-safe
Upstream-Contact:
 SafeLibs maintainers
Source:
 https://tukaani.org/xz
 https://github.com/hasenbanck/lzma-rust2/
Comment:
 This source package contains a Rust implementation of liblzma packaged as a
 drop-in replacement for the Debian liblzma shared-library and development
 packages. It reuses the upstream liblzma public headers, ABI metadata, and
 documentation files from XZ Utils and vendors the lzma-rust2 crate used by the
 Rust port.

